cybersecurity_toolkit/
│
├── .dockerignore                # Files to exclude from Docker image
├── .gitignore                   # Git ignore file
├── Dockerfile                   # Dockerfile to build the container image
├── docker-compose.yaml          # Docker Compose configuration for container orchestration
├── install.sh                   # Bash script to install dependencies
├── requirements.txt             # Python package dependencies
├── README.md                    # Detailed documentation of setup and usage
├── data_structure.py            # Python file for defining tool data structures (optional)
├── main.py                      # Main Python file with the core logic of the toolkit
├── tools/                       # Directory for any additional tool-specific files
│   └── nmap_scan.py             # Tool-specific script or utility for Nmap
│   └── metasploit.py            # Tool-specific script or utility for Metasploit
│   └── hydra_attack.py          # Tool-specific script or utility for Hydra
├── logs/                        # Directory to store logs
│   └── cybersecurity_toolkit.log # Log file for logging errors and activity
└── tools/                       # Directory for any external tool configuration files
